column2: SELECT   S.plate, BC.plate, M.plate, S.fiberID, BC.fiberID, M.fiberID, S.mjd, BC.mjd, M.mjd    INTO   exg_#  FROM   galSpecInfo as S,   stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# as BC,   stellarMassPCAWiscM1# as M  WHERE    S.z_warning=# and S.plateid>=# and S.targettype=&&& and S.spectrotype=&&& and   S.specObjID=BC.specObjID and S.specObjID=M.specObjID
